Package: ImportProquest
Type: Package
Title: A Package to Parse Text Files of Newspaper Articles From ProQuest Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Simon",
           family = "Kiss",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "skiss@wlu.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1837-5428"))
Maintainer: Simon J. Kiss <skiss@wlu.ca>
Description: ProQuest databases are commonly used databases for tracking news articles from a wide variety of sources. They contain a great deal of metadata that can be very useful in text and content analysis in fields like communications, journalistm studies and political science. This package has been built to parse text files downloaded from ProQuest databases to get them ready for analysis in packages such as the `tm` or `quanteda` packages in R. 
